            "title": "盤中速報 - 雙鍵(4764)股價拉至漲停，漲停價128.5元，成交1,927張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鍵(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4764:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4764\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4764-TW</a>)01日11:50上漲11.5元，股價漲停報128.5元，委買2張、委賣58張，成交1,927張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為塑膠添加劑及UV光固化產品等產品之研發、製造與銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鍵(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4764:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4764\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4764-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌9.3%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌2.73%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+162 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+132 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+31 張</li> <li>融資增減：+24 張</li> <li>融券增減：+2 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
