x\"><p>旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)：全球頂尖探針卡廠，VPC 在高階測試領域市佔率高，台積電 CoWoS 擴產帶動的測試介面需求。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>汎銓 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6830:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6830\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6830-TW</a>)：材料分析 (MA)、故障分析 (FA)、表面分析 (SA) 及矽光子檢測服務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>全新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2455:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2455\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2455-TW</a>)： 800G 接收端(PD) 產品高成長。下一代 1.6T 產品 已完成驗證並進入量產階。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>)：亞洲最大 InP 磊晶廠之一。矽光子架構下 CW（連續波）雷射源的重要供應商。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>環宇 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4991:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4991\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4991-TW</a>)：4 吋 InP 晶圓廠產能。主要客戶包含： Innolight、Lumentum 及 Coherent。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IET-KY(<a data-ga-